        "description": "Updated Collection for Vistaprint Clone Backend.\n\n**Modules**:\n- Public API (Users, Catalog, Designs, Orders)\n- Zakeke Integration\n- Admin API\n\n**Auth**: Basic Auth (testuser/password123).",
